<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT64">
<l>pōtāṉa viṭṭiṟaiñci yēttumiṉō poṉmakarak</l>
<l>kātāṉai yātip perumāṉai nātāṉai</l>
<l>nallāṉai nāraṇaṉai nammēḻ piṟappaṟukkuñ</l>
<l>collāṉai colluvatē cūtu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Placing what is [called] flowers and bowing, won’t you extol</l>
<l>Him with gold makara-shaped ear-rings, the primordial Lord,</l>
<l>The Master, the Good [Lord], Nārāyaṇa, Him with words that sever our seven births?</l>
<l>Reciting [them] is [our] means.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
